ivardefs.name: arm_
ivardefs.desc: Describes an expected sequence of events for one of the participants of a study.  E.g. Exposure to drug A, wash-out, exposure to drug B, wash-out, follow-up.

ivardefs.name: category_
ivardefs.desc: Codes categorizing the type of study such as investigational vs. observational, type of blinding, type of randomization, safety vs. efficacy, etc.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in learning more about or engaging with the study.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A full description of how the study is being conducted.

ivardefs.name: enrollment_
ivardefs.desc: Reference to a Group that defines the criteria for and quantity of subjects participating in the study.  E.g. " 200 female Europeans between the ages of 20 and 45 with early onset diabetes".

ivardefs.name: focus_
ivardefs.desc: The condition(s), medication(s), food(s), therapy(ies), device(s) or other concerns or interventions that the study is seeking to gain more information about.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifiers assigned to this research study by the sponsor or other systems.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates a country, state or other region where the study is taking place.

ivardefs.name: keyword_
ivardefs.desc: Key terms to aid in searching for or filtering the study.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Comments made about the event by the performer, subject or other participants.

ivardefs.name: partOf_
ivardefs.desc: A larger research study of which this particular study is a component or step.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the start date and the expected (or actual, depending on status) end date for the study.

ivardefs.name: principalInvestigator
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the individual who has primary oversite of the execution of the study.

ivardefs.name: protocol_
ivardefs.desc: The set of steps expected to be performed as part of the execution of the study.

ivardefs.name: reasonStopped
ivardefs.desc: A description and/or code explaining the premature termination of the study.

ivardefs.name: relatedArtifact_
ivardefs.desc: Citations, references and other related documents.

ivardefs.name: site_
ivardefs.desc: Clinic, hospital or other healthcare location that is participating in the study.

ivardefs.name: sponsor
ivardefs.desc: The organization responsible for the execution of the study.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The current state of the study.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive user-friendly label for the study.
